questions.quote: Wait! Wait! Hi! Listen, Ross can I just talk to you for just a second?
Ahh, I don't believe you. I think you don't want them to see you begging me.
It's the woman from the hospital admissions office. She says there's a problem with the form. Oh, god, oh god...
Well, maybe it won't work out. Maybe Ross won't like her personality.
Phoebe, just the idea of pitting one baby against another, I mean, you know, and judging who's cuter just for a trophy...
Dan just moved in downstairs. Yeah, he just got back from like this four-month trek in the Andes. Nice fella.
I'm sorry. See that's the good thing about my job. All the dinosaurs on my table are already dead.
But you have it right there in that file? You could tell us whether it's a boy or a girl? Dayton or Sandrine? Phoebe or Phoebo?
Okay, I have to do something. I mean, I have, I have to stop it!
I hope you don't think I'm crazy but I feel like I was meant to pick this up, do you believe in that kind of thing?
